in the late 30s when he started to write these these stories which became the space beagle.

16:16.660 --> 16:21.120
But I think he goes beyond that. He has a even though he was trained in the pulp tradition I think

16:21.120 --> 16:26.880
he has a more skill. He's more modern perhaps under the influence of the editor John Campbell.

