to overcome the bad parts of human nature before they can defeat the aliens themselves. So I think

16:49.200 --> 16:55.500
this is a step beyond the pulp tradition even though the formulas and the all the intentions

16:55.500 --> 17:01.180
of the story I think are the same as the early pulp magazines. But Van Vogt is able to go beyond that.

