of the concepts of relativity and the Bussard ramjet for instance. The science in the novel

17:58.580 --> 18:05.500
actually makes it extremely realistic. It's one of the more believable of the pure space

18:05.500 --> 18:15.280
epics that's ever been written. The story is essentially that of a colony ship. A ship full

18:15.280 --> 18:21.000
of people I think about 50 people who are traveling to a colony at a nearby star to set up and start

18:21.000 --> 18:29.960
life there. And on the way after they've gone part of the way toward the star the ship runs into a

18:29.960 --> 18:39.260
small nebula of gas which causes the ship to lose its power of deceleration. They cannot decelerate

18:39.260 --> 18:46.740
without causing so much radiation harm that they would they would all be killed. The only way that

18:46.740 --> 18:55.380
