18:55.380 --> 19:00.320
free of gas where they can go outside the ship outside of the protective barriers

19:01.080 --> 19:10.580
and shielding of the ship to repair that deceleration device. The story that develops is that the ship

19:10.580 --> 19:17.560
cannot find a place that is free enough of gas that they can go out and repair the ship

19:17.560 --> 19:25.840
and it keeps on accelerating until it's actually going through galaxies. But no matter how fast

19:25.840 --> 19:31.360
they go they can never go beyond the speed of light because Anderson as we said before is extremely

19:33.000 --> 19:37.140
true to the scientific knowledge of our day and according to the knowledge that we have

19:37.140 --> 19:42.820
faster than light travel is impossible so he has to dream up a method whereby the

19:43.460 --> 19:48.400
