19:48.980 --> 19:55.680
a ship called the Bussard Ramjet to do this. The Bussard Ramjet is not a new idea that was

19:55.680 --> 20:04.240
invented somewhere in the middle of this century. The basic format is that the ship picks up interstellar

20:04.240 --> 20:12.300
gas molecules by the use of a huge electromagnetic web of sorts a force field if you will that

20:12.960 --> 20:18.620
scoops up these interstellar particles and shoots them out the back end. This provides

20:18.620 --> 20:26.400
