21:39.200 --> 21:44.360
theory of relativity is that the speed that time passes is relative to the speed that an object

21:44.360 --> 21:50.560
is moving. If you have two ships traveling through space with ship A traveling faster than ship B

21:51.160 --> 21:57.420
time will be moving slower on ship A than on ship B. In other words the faster a ship moves the

